Package de.feig.FEDM.Core.ReaderCommand Description

Version 5.00.00

Copyright © FEIG ELECTRONIC GmbH, All Rights Reserved.

Internet : http://www.feig.de  

Each Reader command is built by a sequence of command parameters. The values of the parameters can be set with overloaded methods which passes a string from the package de.feig.FEDM.Core.ReaderCommand representing the name of the command parameter. All names of command parameters of all IDENTIFICATION Readers are unified and divided in hierarchical order in groups and subgroups separated by a dot.

For more general information, please refer to the system manual of the Reader.
